cs.SY, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.CV 

The paper deals with the combination of control theory and machine learning for the lateral control of trucks. The paper discusses the use of control barrier functions (CBFs) for safety and supervised learning for performance. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SY (Systems and Control), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.RO (Robotics), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
